{"data":[{"date":"11:11 11/07","title":"Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9: T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/phap-10-bi-ty-so-rat-nho-cach-biet-rat-lon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/275893/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\nS\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt gi\u1ed1ng tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ha-guc-brazil-bi-thiet-quan-nghiem-trong-tai-vong-ban-ket-421-190571.html\" target=\"_blank\">Thomas Meunier d\u00ednh \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2</span>. HLV Martinez v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Nacer Chadli tr\u00e1m c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Moussa Dembele b\u00ean c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil, khi B\u1ec9 &ldquo;d\u1ee5&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ra \u0111\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eeba hi\u1ec3u h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Meunier khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <strong>H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng tung \u0111\u00f2n ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u, Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn &ldquo;c\u00f2 c\u01b0a&rdquo; v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau c\u00f9ng.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Du-am-tran-dau-Phap-vs-Bi-Ty-so-rat-nho,-cach-biet-rat-lon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ec9 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tung \u0111\u00f2n ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt l\u00e0 v\u1eady, c\u00f2n s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Eden Hazard c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f2n hay h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng pha qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Romelu Lukaku, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n kevin De Bruyne c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e1c quen thu\u1ed9c, tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbp ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9. Trong 2 wingback, Chadli th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trong. B\u00ean c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, Dembele ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. Qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c Marouane Fellaini ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, <strong>Ph\u00e1p&hellip; l\u00e0m g\u00ec c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 ph\u00e1</strong>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng cho B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a HLV Martinez g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 chao \u0111\u1ea3o m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n<strong> &ldquo;si\u00eau xe&rdquo; </strong>Kylian Mbappe t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c, r\u1ed3i b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Phap vs Bi Dembele te ca trong phong ngu tan cong Mbappe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/du-am-phap-10-bi-mot-thoi-thuong-cua-bong-da-the-gioi-la-day.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9: Mbappe li\u00ean t\u1ee5c cho Dembele h\u00edt kh\u00f3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/mbappe-tiep-tuc-de-lai-hinh-anh-cuc-xau-vi-thoi-cau-gio-421-190900.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mbappe sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00ec th\u00f3i ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o</span>. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i ch\u1ee5c gi\u00e2y l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p, B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Mbappe ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng &ldquo;b\u00e0y tr\u00f2&rdquo;, khi chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a anh trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb x\u00f3a t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olivier Giroud b\u1ecb ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u00ec li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1edbi th\u00f3i &ldquo;ch\u00e2n g\u1ed7&rdquo;. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1p th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u1eb3ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Giroud ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee9ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng, ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7, <strong>c\u00f2n ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c lo.</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 khi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng im ti\u1ebfng, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9, trong khi Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf &ldquo;th\u00f3i quen&rdquo; ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec1n, d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Thibaut Courtois. <strong>Ph\u00e1p ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 hay, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Giroud bo lo mot so co hoi cua Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Giroud-bo-lo-mot-so-co-hoi-cua-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Giroud c\u00f3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng sao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 san l\u1ea5p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 2 qu\u1ed1c gia s\u00e1t v\u00e1ch nhau, B\u1ec9 lu\u00f4n coi Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh trong m\u1ecdi l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c. D\u00e2n s\u1ed1 k\u00e9m h\u01a1n 6 l\u1ea7n (12 tri\u1ec7u vs 70 tri\u1ec7u), \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t &ldquo;th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng&rdquo; trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin. C\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c th\u1ec3 thao l\u00e0&hellip; <strong>Eddie Merckx</strong>, m\u1ed9t tay \u0111ua xe \u0111\u1ea1p gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 73.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1edbn l\u00ean v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1998, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 coi Zidane l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ed1 1. Hi\u1ec7n nay, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng m\u1eddi m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 s\u1eafm m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n trong BHL &ndash; ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Henry, \u0111ang ng\u00e0y ng\u00e0y d\u1ea1y d\u1ed7 Romelu Lukaku &ndash; ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Ph\u00e1p, khi 9/11 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0o nho\u00e1ng Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap g\u00ec cho B\u1ec9, khi h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0110T \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean m\u00ecnh trong su\u1ed1t chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/boi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng 1 l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 1986, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00ecn g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Les Bleus h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3. Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, &ldquo;th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 s\u1edf socola 2 l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft EURO v\u00e0 World Cup, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &ndash; so v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n n\u0103m 2016.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, B\u1ec9 \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc hi\u1ec7n nay, nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd n\u1eb1m trong t\u00fai Raphael Varane, trong khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n b\u1edfi &ldquo;c\u1eadu b\u00e9&rdquo; 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p. H\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 l\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil ra &ldquo;d\u1ecda&rdquo; G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois, v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1eaby bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 &ldquo;tr\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb s\u00e1t sao&rdquo; kia, m\u00e0 \u1ea9n s\u00e2u trong \u0111\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 san l\u1ea5p. \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, v\u1eabn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n bung s\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Thong-so-Phap.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\">Thua tr\u1eadn, sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ph\u00e1p &ldquo;ph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vao-chung-ket-nguoi-dan-paris-do-ra-duong-di-bao-421-190905.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/phap-vao-chung-ket-nguoi-dan-paris-do-ra-duong-di-bao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vao-chung-ket-nguoi-dan-paris-do-ra-duong-di-bao-421-190905.html\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Paris \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i b\u00e3o</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0103n m\u1eebng r\u1ea5t cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1137","checkdouble":"190914"},{"date":"09:21 11/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Umtiti n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/umtiti-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti t\u1ecf ra vui m\u1eebng khi gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;\"=\"\">Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;\"=\"\">\u00a0<br>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/umtiti-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Umtiti \u0103n m\u1eebng sau pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00fang v\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho NHM m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u00e0n l\u00f3e s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti. Trong pha l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 5 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtouis ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus n\u00f3i: \u201c\u0110\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi B\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00f4i m\u1edbi xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd d\u00e2ng cao h\u01a1n, tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ho\u1eb7c ch\u1edd b\u00f3ng n\u1ea3y ra. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3, l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Umtiti t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n khi cho r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i thay v\u00ec nh\u1eadn c\u00f4ng lao v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh. \u201cT\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 k\u00edn k\u1ebd trong su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\u201d, trung v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft sau 12 n\u0103m tuy nhi\u00ean Umtiti c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n\u00a0\u2018tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t\u2019 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. B\u00e0i h\u1ecdc th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i EURO 2016 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0y th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190916.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190916.html\">Eden Hazard xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T B\u1ec9 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\">Thua tr\u1eadn, sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ph\u00e1p \u201cph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d</span><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\">HLV Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nHLV Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho Paul Pogba sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u00eam qua.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1136","checkdouble":"190915"},{"date":"10:13 11/07","title":"V\u00ec sao Mbappe v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft World Cup d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 2 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/vi-sao-mbappe-van-duoc-da-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-du-phai-nhan-2-the-vang-lien-tiep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y song anh v\u1eabn s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u00fd do cho chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u00ec sao Mbappe v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft World Cup khi nh\u1eadn 2 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u00ec sao Mbappe v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft World Cup khi nh\u1eadn 2 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Vi-sao-Mbappe-van-duoc-da-chung-ket-World-Cup-khi-nhan-2-the-vang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Mbappe nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng sau chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mbappe \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ch\u1ecbu thua k\u00e9m c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 tinh ranh khi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Uruguay, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u00ec l\u1ed7i c\u00e2u gi\u1edd. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Uruguay t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t b\u1ee9c x\u00fac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha c\u00e2u gi\u1edd l\u1ed9 li\u1ec5u khi c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n pha n\u00e9m bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 90+3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 2 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u song Mbappe v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo lu\u1eadt m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a FIFA, c\u00e1c th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng c\u0169 s\u1ebd\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00f3a khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Les Bleus \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190916.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190916.html\">Eden Hazard xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T B\u1ec9 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/umtiti-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190915.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/umtiti-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/umtiti-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190915.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Umtiti n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p?</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti t\u1ecf ra vui m\u1eebng khi gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ha-guc-bi-pogba-gianh-chien-thang-cho-doi-bong-thai-lan-421-190899.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/ha-guc-bi-pogba-gianh-chien-thang-cho-doi-bong-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ha-guc-bi-pogba-gianh-chien-thang-cho-doi-bong-thai-lan-421-190899.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c B\u1ec9, Pogba gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan</span><br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba tri \u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1135","checkdouble":"190920"},{"date":"10:02 11/07","title":"\u0110T Anh nh\u1eadn tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/dt-anh-nhan-tin-vui-truoc-tran-dai-chien-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Croatia, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin vui khi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Henderson v\u00e0 Jamie Vardy \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Croatia tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Luzhniki v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin vui v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 khi hai ng\u00f4i sao Henderson v\u00e0 Vardy l\u00e0 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ngay sau khi \u0111\u00e1p chuy\u1ebfn bay xu\u1ed1ng Moscow t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh Repino. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Henderson g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 g\u00e2n kheo trong khi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Jamie Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Henderson DT Anh\" title=\"tien ve Henderson DT Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/sao-liverpool-bi-phe-truat-ngoi-thu-quan-anh-ngay-truoc-them-chung-ket-c1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Henderson l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Tam S\u01b0 b\u1edfi Henderson \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, trong khi Jamie Vardy v\u1eabn l\u00e0 &lsquo;qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng&rsquo; v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Croatia b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e9 l\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Southgate s\u1ebd gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t nh\u01b0 khi \u0110T Anh \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua. S\u1edf d\u0129, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 47 l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 do \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef v\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a HLV Southgate, \u0110T anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 3-5-2. Tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford. Kyle Walker, John Stones, Harry Maguire s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. 5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 g\u1ed3m Kieran Trippier, Jordan Henderson, Jesse Lingard, Dele Alli, Ashley Young. Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Sterling \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i khi m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, anh c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng HLV Southgate v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1ea5y ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 k\u00e9o d\u00e3n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Anh vs Croatia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h00 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai 12/7. Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:&#10;16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7): V\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1?</span><br>\r\n28 n\u0103m l\u1ebb m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eb5ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay &ndash; B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup, m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t Croatia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pickford-la-chia-khoa-giup-anh-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190881.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/pickford-la-chia-khoa-giup-anh-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pickford-la-chia-khoa-giup-anh-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190881.html\">&ldquo;Pickford l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a gi\u00fap Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nFabio Capello ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford, c\u1ef1u HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Everton s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-va-modric-se-giup-croatia-danh-bai-anh-421-190875.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/rakitic-va-modric-se-giup-croatia-danh-bai-anh.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-va-modric-se-giup-croatia-danh-bai-anh-421-190875.html\">Rakitic v\u00e0 Modric s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh</span><br>\r\nFilip Tapalovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh, c\u1ef1u sao Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tam s\u01b0 nh\u1edd b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Luka Modric v\u00e0 Ivan Rakitic.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1134","checkdouble":"190921"},{"date":"10:48 11/07","title":"Kevin De Bruyne cay c\u00fa v\u00ec c\u00e1ch th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/kevi-de-bruyne-cay-cu-vi-cach-thang-cua-dt-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Kevin De Bruyne kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p khi cho r\u1eb1ng B\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0110T B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u00f4m h\u1eadn. D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 v\u1edbi pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Samuel Umtiti. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup (1986 v\u00e0 2018), \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i l\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai k\u1ef3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u thua ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p*.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kevin De Bruyne cay c\u00fa v\u00ec c\u00e1ch th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kevin De Bruyne cay c\u00fa v\u00ec c\u00e1ch th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/kevi-de-bruyne-cay-cu-vi-cach-thang-cua-dt-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Kevi De Bruyne cay c\u00fa v\u00ec c\u00e1ch th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Kevin De Bruyne kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh &quot;qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot; kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i: &quot;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc 'b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd'? C\u00f3 l\u1ebd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c \u0110T Ph\u00e1p<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u, Kevin De Bruyne kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n m\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">De Bruyne cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 th\u1ebf&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ef1c cao v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ebd ra ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, d\u00f9 Ph\u00e1p ch\u1eb3ng ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i thua trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa Croatia vs Anh v\u00e0o 21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>* N\u0103m 1986, B\u1ec9 thua Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190916.html\">Eden Hazard xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/tien-ve-pogba-chia-se-chien-thang-truoc-bi-cung-doi-bong-nhi-vua-duoc-giai-cuu-188-190908.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba chia s\u1ebb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ed v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\">Thua tr\u1eadn, sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ph\u00e1p &ldquo;ph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vao-chung-ket-nguoi-dan-paris-do-ra-duong-di-bao-421-190905.html\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Paris \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i b\u00e3o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\">HLV Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-tiep-tuc-de-lai-hinh-anh-cuc-xau-vi-thoi-cau-gio-421-190900.html\">Sau tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau \u0103n v\u1ea1, Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ef1c x\u1ea5u v\u00ec th\u00f3i c\u00e2u gi\u1edd</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1133","checkdouble":"190922"},{"date":"11:42 11/07","title":"World Cup 2018: Nike \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Adidas d\u00f9 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn chung k\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/world-cup-2018-nike-danh-bai-adidas.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng Nike \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Adidas m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Adidas \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nike.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nike \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Adidas<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng Nike \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Adidas x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1. Trong s\u1ed1 4 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Adidas ch\u1ec9 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 cho B\u1ec9 - \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"World Cup 2018 Nike \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Adidas d\u00f9 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn chung k\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"World Cup 2018 Nike \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Adidas d\u00f9 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn chung k\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/world-cup-2018-nike-danh-bai-adidas.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nike \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Adidas d\u00f9 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \"n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn\" c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u Nike, b\u1edfi c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa Croatia v\u00e0 Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nike. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi Nike khi h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf so v\u1edbi Adidas trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adidas ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n thua<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ecb Nike \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, Adidas v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 thua. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, Adidas v\u1eabn th\u1eafng l\u1edbn khi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 ch\u00ednh cho World Cup 2018. Tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng Telstar 18 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Adidas x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c Adidas tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a FIFA su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1970 \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u00e0 s\u1ebd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2030 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap h\u00e3ng \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng thua so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 World Cup. D\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng trung b\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, Adidas ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1eeb 25 \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u USD cho FIFA.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Nike t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u cho Iran v\u00ec l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn h\u00e3ng \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9 m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Adidas s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng m\u1edf c\u1eeda v\u1edbi Iran gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi FIFA trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 sau n\u0103m 2030. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd FIFA lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1 cao kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u00e1ch b\u1ea1ch v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, World Cup 2018 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Adidas.\r\n<h2><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-don-gian-khien-phap-da-bai-dt-bi-o-ban-ket-world-cup-421-190927.html\">3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-nhan-tin-vui-truoc-tran-dai-chien-croatia-421-190921.html\">\u0110T Anh nh\u1eadn tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vi-sao-mbappe-van-duoc-da-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-du-phai-nhan-2-the-vang-lien-tiep-421-190920.html\">V\u00ec sao Mbappe v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft World Cup d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 2 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190916.html\">Eden Hazard xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/umtiti-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190915.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Umtiti n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-10-bi-ty-so-rat-nho-cach-biet-rat-lon-421-190914.html\">Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9: T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1132","checkdouble":"190925"},{"date":"11:23 11/07","title":"3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/3-ly-do-don-gian-khien-phap-da-bai-dt-bi-o-ban-ket-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u00edt h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng song b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4n ngoan \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Deschamps \u0111i ti\u1ebfp?</h2><h2>1. S\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Thomas Meunier<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5m th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t tai h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i Thomas Meunier \u0111\u00e0nh ph\u1ea3i l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>V\u00e0 Meunier c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay th\u1ebf Thomas Meunier, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Nacer Chadli \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i PSG \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/3-ly-do-don-gian-khien-Phap-danh-bai-Bi-o-ban-ket-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u1ec9 suy y\u1ebfu khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Meunier</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nacer Chadli v\u00e0 Mousa Dembele ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 khi HLV Roberto Martinez r\u00fat Dembele kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng Dries Mertens.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 n\u00e9t h\u01a1n cho \u0110T B\u1ec9, tuy nhi\u00ean qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2.\u00a0D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Deschamps<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u x\u00f4ng x\u00e1o\u00a0v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Martinez b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed b\u1ed9 ba Fellaini \u2013 Dembele \u2013 Witsel ch\u01a1i gi\u0103ng ngang nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, Hazard tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong hi\u1ec7p 1 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i B\u1ec9 c\u00e0ng sa l\u1ea7y v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u v\u00e0 c\u00e1i b\u1eaby m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1o ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 cao tay h\u01a1n khi b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Matuidi v\u00e0 Kante thay nhau ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9. B\u1ecb theo k\u00e8m nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng, vi\u1ec7c Hazard kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Deschamps\" title=\"Deschamps\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/phap-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-su-khung-bo-cua-didier-deschamps.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi chia c\u1eaft c\u00e1c m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Hazard b\u1ecb chia c\u1eaft khi\u1ebfn De Bruyne ch\u1eb3ng bi\u1ebft ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng ai c\u00f2n Lukaku v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00f3i b\u00f3ng. B\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 cao tay h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 Varane v\u00e0 Umtiti\u00a0v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp trung nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Pogba, Giroud, Griezmann c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u00e0 Deschamp \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u2018\u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 t\u00f4ng\u2019 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Lloris<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ea7y c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng v\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Hugo Lloris qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung g\u1ed7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 22 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hugo Lloris c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t World Cup n\u0103m nay tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Toby Alderweireld.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lloris\" title=\"Lloris\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/hugo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Lloris \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau pha l\u1ed9n x\u1ed9n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, Alderweireld \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa xoay ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c nhanh v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ed9t r\u1eebng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 bay v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa khung th\u00e0nh.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Lloris.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ecb che m\u1eaft b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp \u0111\u01b0a tay c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ef1c nhanh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. N\u1ebfu Lloris kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Alderweireld m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho B\u1ec9, c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c b\u1edfi Eden Hazard v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eebng gi\u00fap h\u1ecd qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ebf m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y, pha c\u1ee9u thua c\u1ee7a Hugo Lloris c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Samuel Umtiti.\u00a0 V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 31 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1131","checkdouble":"190927"},{"date":"11:41 11/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 11/7: Juventus \u0111\u00f3n Ronaldo, M.U thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i s\u1edf h\u1eefu Mandzukic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/ngay-hom-nay-117.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (11/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus \u0111\u00f3n Ronaldo, M.U thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i s\u1edf h\u1eefu Mandzukic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, t\u1edd Mirror \u0111\u01b0a tin MU s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mario Mandzukic nh\u1edd v\u00e0o \u201cv\u1eadt t\u1ebf\u201d Matteo Darmian. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 32 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng t\u0103ng sau khi Ronaldo v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.\u00a0 Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Mourinho r\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Mandzukic v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u201cchia l\u1eeda\u201d tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Romelu Lukaku. Do v\u1eady, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 117, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 117, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/khong-phai-modric-hay-rakitic-linh-hon-cua-croatia-la-ai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mario Mandzukic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\"Bom t\u1ea5n\" Mahrez c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Man City \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Riyad Mahrez t\u1eeb Leicester City. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ebfn Man City v\u1edbi ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a CLB. Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u00e1o s\u1ed1 26 t\u1eeb Man Xanh. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi CLB. Trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, Mahrez c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 HLV Pep Guardiola. Mahrez th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Guardiola l\u00e0 m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a anh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\">Man City CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mahrez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Qua \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Lucas Torreira trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup. Song ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi khi Uruguay r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, Torreira m\u1edbi sang London \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. H\u00f4m qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Arsenal. Torreira \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Arsenal, nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 120.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. T\u1ea1i Emirates, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 11 c\u1ee7a Mesut Oezil. \u0110\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Torreira, Arsenal ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho Sampdoria 30 tri\u1ec7u euro (26,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-xac-nhan-co-tan-binh-thu-4-tri-gia-30-trieu-euro-172-190886.html\">Arsenal CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Juventus s\u1eafp gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u1edd The Mirror cho bi\u1ebft trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea ngay sau khi Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri thay th\u1ebf Antonio Conte. Rugani, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Chelsea 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a David Luiz v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho HLV Sarri \u1edf CLB Empoli tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1ec1 Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 117 Juventus \u0111\u00f3n Ronaldo, MU thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i s\u1edf h\u1eefu Mandzukic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 117 Juventus \u0111\u00f3n Ronaldo, MU thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i s\u1edf h\u1eefu Mandzukic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-117-Juventus-don-Ronaldo,-MU-thuan-loi-so-huu-Mandzukic-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rugani</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Ospina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David Ospina s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Boca Juniors \u1edf Argentina v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. T\u1edd The Mirror cho bi\u1ebft m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal nh\u01b0ng Ospina quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i do Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno t\u1eeb Leverkusen v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Petr Cech \u0111\u00e3 cao tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<h2>Barca s\u1eafp b\u00e1n sao Colombia cho Everton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo t\u1edd Goal, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp \u0111ang t\u00ednh chia tay Yerry Mina. Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n cho \u0110T Colombia \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00e9o \u0110T Anh v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 khi \u201cThe Toffees\u201d s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 24 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"yerry mina cua Colombia\" title=\"yerry mina cua Colombia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Tottenham-va-Everton-muon-mua-Yerry-Mina-cua-Barcelona-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea quy\u1ebft ph\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1m Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ph\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1m \u0110KV\u0110 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong v\u1ee5 mua Jorginho khi nh\u1edd HLV Maurizio Sarri thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf Napoli c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn London. \u201cThe Blues\u201d c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng 60 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t The Citizens. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1130","checkdouble":"190933"},{"date":"11:53 11/07","title":"\u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f3 tin, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/7/uy-ban-olympic-chau-a-mac-sai-lam-kho-tin-mon-bong-da-nam-co-the-phai-boc-tham-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Vi\u1ec7c \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA) qu\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean hai qu\u1ed1c gia UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3&nbsp;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra. Theo \u0111\u00f3 danh s\u00e1ch 24 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f3 tin, K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f3 tin, K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Mac-sai-lam-kho-tin,-Ket-qua-boc-tham-ASIAD-2018-co-the-phai-boc--hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018 thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t UAE v\u00e0 Palestine</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u1ee6y ban Olympic Qu\u1ed1c gia UAE \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd tham d\u1ef1 \u1edf n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u1ee6y ban Olympic Qu\u1ed1c gia UAE, \u00f4ng Ahmed Al Tayeb \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi UAE kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Palestine.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn 100% l\u00e0 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Indonesia. Kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u sao ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o trong danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m. T\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1, BTC gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n xem x\u00e9t l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng c\u1ea3nh ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi UAE c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0110T Olympic Palestine khi n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y c\u0169ng b\u1ecb BTC &lsquo;b\u1ecf r\u01a1i&rsquo; kh\u1ecfi m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 OCA v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng l\u1ea1i hay ph\u00e2n UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o 2 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p khi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-u23-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-190502.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/7/cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-u23-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-u23-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-190502.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018, hai chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-183020.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-183020.html\">V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 Asiad 2018?</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Jordan v\u1eeba qua ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Asiad 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c danh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1129","checkdouble":"190939"},{"date":"07:20 11/07","title":"Mbappe: \"Qu\u00ean Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng \u0111i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup!\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/mbappe-quen-qua-bong-vang-di-toi-muon-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Mbappe kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a anh l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n nh\u01b0 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng.</h2><h2>Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00eam qua. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc n\u00e0y, coi nh\u01b0 Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMbappe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay. Sao tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng cho danh hi\u1ec7u Ballon d&rsquo;Or khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i teen \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau Pele ghi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup.</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mbappe m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/mbappe-quen-qua-bong-vang-di-toi-muon-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mbappe m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ebb vang tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup, Mbappe kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p thay v\u00ec ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng vinh quang cho c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00ecnh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>&ldquo;C\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a d\u00e1m m\u01a1 t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd th\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111ang m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Khi b\u1ea1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng gian l\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00ec t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng. Khi n\u00e0o t\u00f4i c\u00f2n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup!&rdquo;.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-phap-10-bi-421-190892.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1128","checkdouble":"190902"},{"date":"07:14 11/07","title":"\u201cVua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d Pele ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/pele-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-quyet-dinh-sang-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real Madrid sang Juventus. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cVua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb Real Madrid. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ph\u00eda Juve \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Liverpool, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Los Blancos sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/pele-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-quyet-dinh-sang-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pele c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng cho Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &ldquo;Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo; b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u cho h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Pele t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua 18 n\u0103m \u1edf Santos tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o New York Cosmos.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus-180-190857.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus-180-190857.html\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus?</span><br>\r\n<span>Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Xin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng, Cristiano&rdquo;, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. &ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Santos song \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chia tay, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 15 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Real. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 4 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 5 m\u00f9a qua. Trong 9 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los Blancos, anh ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 438 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e2y l\u00e0m b\u00e0n v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-nham-sao-khung-mu-thay-ronaldo-180-190887.html\">Real nh\u1eafm sao kh\u1ee7ng MU thay Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/david-trezeguet-noi-gi-ve-thuong-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-176-190885.html\">David Trezeguet n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/emre-can-hao-huc-truoc-co-hoi-choi-bong-cung-ronaldo-184-190838.html\">T\u00e2n binh Juventus h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/buffon-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-juve-chieu-mo-ronaldo-421-190836.html\">Buffon n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Juve chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1127","checkdouble":"190910"},{"date":"08:03 11/07","title":"Pogba: \"Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Euro 2016\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/croatia-tu-davor-suker-den-luca-mondric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup tr\u00f4i qua t\u1ea7m tay khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Euro 2016.</h2><h2>Pogba hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 v\u1eeba qua. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Umtiti nh\u01b0ng Pogba v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf Euro 2016. V\u00e0 anh m\u1edbi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng Les Bleus s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pogba hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/croatia-tu-davor-suker-den-luca-mondric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;L\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0 Euro 2016. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Euro nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang. V\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y tr\u00f4i qua th\u00eam n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. N\u0103m 2016, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i vui v\u00ec m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m c\u00e1c C\u0110V vui h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam 15/7 t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Pogba d\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu ni\u00ean Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t \u1edf hang Tham Luang su\u1ed1t 2 tu\u1ea7n qua. Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 13 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hang \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb ng\u1eadp cho t\u1edbi t\u1eadn th\u00e1ng 10.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch FIFA Gianni Infantino c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft th\u01b0 cho Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 m\u1eddi 12 c\u1eadu nh\u00f3c c\u00f9ng HLV t\u1edbi xem tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 ngay cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1126","checkdouble":"190911"},{"date":"08:58 11/07","title":"Eden Hazard xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T B\u1ec9 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</h2><h2>B\u1ec9 v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng World Cup sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n sao h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7y m\u00ea ho\u1eb7c. Ph\u00e1p nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n khi d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb B\u1ec9 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01a1i l\u00e9p v\u00e9, B\u1ec9 d\u1ea7n l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi uy hi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong hi\u1ec7p 2. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. </p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phap vs Bi\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/boi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1eeda thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sau m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Umtiti \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 51 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o ra b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t l\u1edbn cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u1ec9 n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Eden Hazard xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p theo k\u00e8m r\u1ea5t ch\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T B\u1ec9 Eden Hazard c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. Ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ecf ra nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi &lsquo;m\u1ea5t h\u00fat&rsquo; trong hi\u1ec7p 2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua, Hazard th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng n\u00f3i: &ldquo;B\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n, khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed9i c\u00f3 hai c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 n\u00e9t, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lloris \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard\" title=\"Eden Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Eden Hazard&nbsp;xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00eam B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. D\u1eabu sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i hay nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng may \u0111\u00e3 thua m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh&rdquo;, Hazard chia s\u1ebb trong ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Hazard v\u1eabn ch\u00fac m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Anh c\u0169ng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Les Bleus s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng sau tr\u00f2n 2 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\">Thua tr\u1eadn, sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ph\u00e1p &ldquo;ph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\">HLV Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nHLV Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho Paul Pogba sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u00eam qua.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tran-tranh-hang-3-cua-dt-bi-dien-ra-khi-nao-421-190898.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/tran-tranh-hang-3-cua-dt-bi-dien-ra-khi-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tran-tranh-hang-3-cua-dt-bi-dien-ra-khi-nao-421-190898.html\">Tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 di\u1ec5n ra khi n\u00e0o?</span><br>\r\nLukaku v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t &ldquo;tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng&rdquo; n\u1eefa. V\u1eady tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/Deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-dau-Phap-1-0-Bi-ban-ket-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1125","checkdouble":"190916"},{"date":"04:56 11/07","title":"Man City CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mahrez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Qua \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mahrez t\u1eeb Leicester City. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a The Citizens trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u00fang ra h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 Mahrez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man City c\u00f3 ra s\u1ee9c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u, Leicester c\u0169ng gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Mahrez d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ee9c 95 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m Philippe Coutinho, ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1eddi Liverpool \u0111\u1ebfn Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 142 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mahrez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mahrez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Man-City-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-Mahrez-voi-gia-60-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mahrez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMahrez bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Leicester d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed9p \u0111\u01a1n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u201ch\u1ed1i h\u1eadn\u201d v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed9c mua b\u00e1n di\u1ec5n ra. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p Anh, \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMahrez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u00e2n cho Leicester v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao. K\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a 2017/18, anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 10 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, gi\u00fap B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch Premier League \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 9. C\u00f2n Man City, h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 100 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00f2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"mahrez va vardy\" title=\"mahrez va vardy\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marez l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Leicester 4 n\u0103m qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, Man City v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Mahrez c\u00f9ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Champions League. H\u1ecd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Mahrez v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1eafn \u0111o, Leicester \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. Mahrez nhanh ch\u00f3ng di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Etihad ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n y t\u1ebf b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi CLB m\u1edbi. <br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 Mahrez t\u1ea1i Leicester:</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- Mahrez gia nh\u1eadp Leicester t\u1eeb Le Havre v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 400 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng n\u0103m 2014, b\u1eb1ng 1/150 l\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Man City m\u1edbi b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh.<br>\r\n- Sau 179 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Leicester, Mahrez ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 48 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham (214) v\u00e0 Wilfried Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace (234) l\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 pha qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Mahrez (176) m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n- T\u1eeb khi Mahrez ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014, ch\u1ec9 8 ng\u01b0\u1eddi (Eden Hazard, Diego Costa, Eriksen, Jamie Vardy, Alexis Sanchez, Romelu Lukaku, Sergio Aguero v\u00e0 Harry Kane) l\u00e0 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-man-city-172-190593.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/toi-luot-man-city-vao-cuoc-vu-hang-hot-world-cup-2018-172-190594.html\">T\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Man City v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng hot World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-2-ben-do-tiem-nang-cua-pep-sau-khi-roi-man-city-172-190504.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 2 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pep sau khi r\u1eddi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-sap-cong-bo-bom-tan-43-trieu-bang-172-190354.html\">Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 bom t\u1ea5n 43 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1124","checkdouble":"190895"},{"date":"05:07 11/07","title":"HLV Martinez chia s\u1ebb l\u00fd do g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/hlv-martinez-chia-se-ly-do-guc-nga-truoc-dt-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Roberto Martinez chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2>B\u1ec9 thua v\u00ec b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. H\u1ecd th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, sau pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti, qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a &ldquo;th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng&rdquo; tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, khi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. D\u00f9 r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng HLV Roberto Martinez c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i. S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Roberto Martinez chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p\" title=\"Martinez chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/hlv-martinez-chia-se-ly-do-guc-nga-truoc-dt-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Roberto Martinez chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00f9i s\u00e2u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u, ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u00fac h\u1ecd nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Roberto Martinez chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thua \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng World Cup 2018 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Eden Hazard v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u1edbi \u0110T Croatia/Anh v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe-421-190894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe-421-190894.html\">Ferdinand tr\u00f2n m\u1eaft: L\u00e0m th\u1ebf qu\u00e1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mbappe?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Rio Ferdinand ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 Mbappe v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd ma thu\u1eadt.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1123","checkdouble":"190896"}]}